{
  "title": "Xenial Grilled Croatian Seafood Stew",
  "description": "A fresh and pillowy Croatian dish featuring lamb stock and char-grilled seafood, perfect for a brunch mood. This pescatarian-friendly stew is cooked in a cataplana vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
