      "name": "parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together lamb stock, garlic, and lemon juice.",
    "Add the shrimp, mussels, and clams to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Brush the cataplana vessel with olive oil and add the seafood mixture.",
    "Close the cataplana and place it on the grill, cooking for 10 minutes.",
    "Open the cataplana and stir in chopped parsley.",
    "Return the cataplana to the grill and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the cataplana from the grill and let it cool for a few minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
